articles.title: Xiao Qi's Visual Analytics Site for ISSS608
articles.description:
Welcome to my website where I compile all the take home exercises and dataviz makeover assignments for ISSS608 Visual Analytics and   Applications under SMU MITB program, by Prof Kam Tin Seong.

Feel free to reach out to me at xiaoqilee.2020@mitb.smu.edu.sg should you have any feedback or need any clarification.

Enjoy & Stay Safe!
